              h4 #[span.fw-lighter Predict &amp; Calculate]#[br]Protein Properties
            .col-6.col-md-4.order-2.order-md-first
              a.link-darken.d-block.position-relative(href="/protein-parameters/") !{filters.image( filters.url("/images/science/protein-parameters.svg"), "Predict Protein Parameters" )}
            .col-12.col-md-8.offset-md-4.order-last
              p A future update of the MS/MS database application #[a(href="https://doi.org/10.1186/1471-2105-9-302" target="_blank") 2DB] was supposed to have numerous little functions helping to quickly characterize proteins identified by mass spectrometry.
              p The functions, originally in PHP, have found a new home here.
              a.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-secondary(href="/protein-parameters/") #[i.bi.bi-calculator] Calculate Parameters

        .col-12.col-md-6.my-md-5.my-3
          .row
            .col-12.col-md-8.order-first.order-md-2
              h4 #[span.fw-lighter Predict &amp; Calculate]#[br]Chlorophyll Content
            .col-6.col-md-4.order-2.order-md-first
              a.link-darken.d-block.position-relative(href="/chlorophyll-content/") !{filters.image( filters.url("/images/science/chlorophyll.svg"), "Calculate Chlorophyll Content" )}
            .col-12.col-md-8.offset-md-4.order-last
              p Working with plants or algae provides the option to use either total protein content or chlorophyll content for the planned experiment.
              p This calculator allows calculating the chlorophyll content according to Porra et al.
              a.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-secondary(href="/chlorophyll-content/") #[i.bi.bi-calculator]  Calculate Content


