            .col-6.col-md-4.order-2.order-md-first
              a.link-darken.d-block.position-relative(href="/format-fasta/") !{filters.image( filters.url("/images/science/fasta.svg"), "Format FASTA file output" )}
            .col-12.col-md-8.offset-md-4.order-last
              p Formatting a DNA/RNA or AminoAcid sequence can be a pain, especially if you only have to do it occasionally and you don't have those fancy tools.
              p This tool you allows to quickly format your sequence to fit your needed layout.
              a.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-secondary(href="/format-fasta/") #[i.bi.bi-chevron-right] Format FASTA

