            .col-6.col-md-4.order-2.order-md-first
              a.link-darken.d-block.position-relative(href="/formatted-citation/") !{filters.image( filters.url("/images/science/doi.svg"), "Get formated Citiation by DOI" )}
            .col-12.col-md-8.offset-md-4.order-last
              p Originally part of a simple function made for the PhotosynQ platform to add references, this form can now be used to receive a formatted citation.
              p No need to fire up your reference manager, a DOI number is enough.
              a.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-secondary(href="/formatted-citation/") #[i.bi.bi-quote] Get Citation

  section
    .container
