        .col-12.my-5
          .row
            .col-12.col-md-10.order-first.order-md-2
              h4 #[span.fw-lighter From Before the New Millenium]#[br]Jugend Forscht
            .col-6.col-md-2.order-2.order-md-first
              a.link-darken.d-block.position-relative(href="/jugend-forscht/") !{filters.image( filters.url("/images/jugend-forscht/jugend-forscht.svg"), "Jugend Forscht" )}
            .col-12.col-md-10.offset-md-2.order-last
              p
                | #[a(href="https://www.jugend-forscht.de/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" lang="de-DE") Jugend forscht] (Youth researches) is a German
                | competition in the areas of science, technology, engineering, and mathematics (STEM) which two friends and I entered in high school back in 1999.
                | This is the work we did on identifying different leaf pigments over the course of a year in #[i Parthenocissus tricuspidata], titled
                | #[em(lang="de-DE") &quot;Die Wilden Farben des Wilden Weins&quot;] - #[em &quot;The Various Colors of Boston Ivy&quot;].
